  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436210/extras/ab429b13cdf80aacec715548b82fb1b6.poster.avif?t=1620138086\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436210/extras/ab429b13cdf80aacec715548b82fb1b6.webm?t=1620138086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436210/extras/ab429b13cdf80aacec715548b82fb1b6.mp4?t=1620138086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore and escape twisting realms in this dark action puzzle game. Delving through surreal landscapes pocketed throughout the cathedral, Isaiah must confront his deadly sins by warding them off in unique worlds and boss battles. Discover new tools to help you through your journey, and uncover Isaiah's past sins to escape purgatory!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436210/extras/031db7b9691b91aacb28cce5fce9cbbf.poster.avif?t=1620138086\" width=700 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436210/extras/031db7b9691b91aacb28cce5fce9cbbf.webm?t=1620138086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436210/extras/031db7b9691b91aacb28cce5fce9cbbf.mp4?t=1620138086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore and Escape the seven levels of Isaiah's personal hell<br></li><li> Outwit monstrous demons and overcome puzzling trials<br></li><li> Find useful tools to help you along your journey and interact with your surroundings<br></li><li> Platform through unique environments inspired by Isaiah's past<br></li><li> Overcome Isaiah's dark past and ultimately decide his fate</li></ul>",
